    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The shadow side is a classic Moria Swarms  with Armories and 2 There are coming because of Albert ; It&#39;s backed up by nazgul skills which let us overwheming our opponents easily.<br />
It&#39; s important to play a few gobs in the first sites to use efficiently the hosts ...<br />
<br />
The Free People side is more interesting because of the general strategy : It&#39;s a small fellowship based on gandalf skills and archery.<br />
You have just to accept that the fellowship exits only to let the shadow wins. In fact the Capacities of Elrond and Gandalf must be used all the time to give you a good card advantage...<br />
<br />
Finally, you must know when and how you want to kill a companion, according to that, try to keep fire for the good oppportunity (for example dimril dale )<br />
<br />
Have Fun !!<br />
<br />
Please, give construtive criticizes...Thanks<br />
